videos.description: Grant Williams with good positioning in the paint gets the bank shot to go over the defender.
videos.headline: Williams powers in basket for Tennessee

videos.description: Nick Weatherspoon picks up the loose ball and takes it up the court for the fast-break score.
videos.headline: Mississippi State's Weatherspoon goes coast-to-coast

videos.description: Quinndary Weatherspoon swats away the 3-pointer attempt from Jordan Bowden for Mississippi State.
videos.headline: Weatherspoon rejects shot into stands

videos.description: Quinndary Weatherspoon drives through defenders and gets the layup to go plus the foul.
videos.headline: Weatherspoon gets the tough and-1 layup

videos.description: Nick Weatherspoon goes to the floor grabbing his hip after contact under the basket. On an ensuing fast-break steal, Weatherspoon is involved in another collision. Both teams show their support as Weatherspoon is carted off on a stretcher.
videos.headline: Weatherspoon carted off on stretcher after collision

videos.description: Eli Wright picks off the pass then takes it up the court for the and-1 layup.
videos.headline: Wright lays in fast-break steal for Bulldogs

videos.description: Admiral Schofield gets the pass at the wing then hits the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Schofield knocks down 3-pointer

videos.description: Jordan Bone drives to the basket and scores on the nice reverse layup.
videos.headline: Bone makes reverse layup for Tennessee

videos.description: Quinndary Weatherspoon grabs the missed shot then lays it back in plus the foul.
videos.headline: Weatherspoon gets the and-1 putback layup

videos.description: Tennessee's Lamonte Turner forces the steal then scores the easy fast-break layup.
videos.headline: Turner scores on fast-break layup

videos.description: Lamar Peters drives to the basket then passes over to Xavian Stapleton in the corner who misses the 3-pointer that would have given the Bulldogs in the lead in the final seconds.
videos.headline: Mississippi State's go-ahead 3-pointer is off target

videos.description: Tennessee edges Mississippi State 62-59 and advances to the SEC semifinals.
videos.headline: Vols hold off Bulldogs
